sequenceDiagram
    actor You as You (editor)
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant Watch as chokidar
    participant Main as Main process
    participant Render as Renderer
    You->>FS: save document.md
    FS-->>Watch: change event
    Watch->>Main: file changed
    Main->>Render: vv:content { path, kind, text / bytes }
    Render->>Render: re-render (keep scroll, tabs, history)
    Render-->>You: preview repaints in place
